OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: The votes are
OL,4,Cbeing counted in the showdown for
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FVotes will be counted across Sussex
OL,8,Fafter hundreds of thousands went to
OL,9,Fthe polls, to vote for their new
OL,10,Fcouncillors.
OL,12,FIn East and West Sussex, elections
OL,13,Fwere held at a county council level,
OL,14,Fas well in some boroughs and districts.
OL,16,FElections should have taken place last
OL,17,Fyear, but they were delayed because of
OL,18,Flocal government reorganisation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
