OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: The votes are
OL,4,Cbeing counted in the showdown for
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FThis is expected to see the current
OL,8,Fcouncil make-up abolished, instead
OL,9,Freplaced with larger unitary
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FUse our interactive map to see the
OL,13,Fresults of each seat in the East
OL,14,FSussex County Council elections.
OL,16,FReform UK, the Conservatives, the
OL,17,FLiberal Democrats, the Greens, and the
OL,18,FLabour Party are all battling for
OL,19,Fcontrol of East Sussex County Council.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
