OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: The votes are
OL,4,Cbeing counted in the showdown for
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FIt's currently run by a minority
OL,8,FConservative administration, and in
OL,9,Frecent weeks we have seen the party
OL,10,Framp up its campaigning in key areas,
OL,11,Fto try to take full control.
OL,13,FBut, Reform UK, which run the
OL,14,Fneighbouring Kent County Council, are
OL,15,Fhopeful they can make gains. They have
OL,16,Fbeen focusing efforts on key areas,
OL,17,Fsuch as Hastings, where there are also
OL,18,Fborough council elections.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
