OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: The votes are
OL,4,Cbeing counted in the showdown for
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FHowever, the Greens are hopeful they
OL,8,Fcan extend gains made in recent years,
OL,9,Fand break the Tory grip on the county.
OL,11,FUse our interactive map to see the
OL,12,Fresults of each seat in the West
OL,13,FSussex County Council elections.
OL,15,FOver in West Sussex, the Conservatives
OL,16,Fhave a stronger grip on the county
OL,17,Fcouncil. All 70 seats up for grabs
OL,18,Fthere, with all parties eyeing control
OL,19,Fof the authority.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
