OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: The votes are
OL,4,Cbeing counted in the showdown for
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrats will be hoping
OL,8,Fto snatch seats from the Tories,
OL,9,Fwhilst the Greens will be hoping to
OL,10,Fmake gains in previously Labour areas.
OL,12,FVoters in the county will also have
OL,13,Fborough elections in some areas, such
OL,14,Fas Adur and Worthing, where Labour
OL,15,Fcould lose control of the smaller
OL,16,Fcouncils there.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
