OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: The votes are
OL,4,Cbeing counted in the showdown for
OL,5,CSussex
OL,7,FMeanwhile up in Crawley, Labour will
OL,8,Fbe hoping to hold the authority,
OL,9,Fdespite recent attempts by the council
OL,10,Fto join the new East Surrey super-
OL,11,Fauthority.
OL,13,FAnd, these could be the last elections
OL,14,Fheld in the current format, as local
OL,15,Fgovernment reorganisation looms.
OL,17,FThis could see the current 15 councils
OL,18,Facross the historic county of Sussex
OL,19,Freplaced with four new unitary
OL,20,Fauthorities.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
